    "content": {
      "rendered": "<h2><strong>Global Trends in Giving Report</strong></h2>\n<p>Released on September 14, 2020, the <a href=\"https://www.funraise.org/giving-report\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>2020 Global Trends in Giving Report</strong></a> examines how donors prefer to give and engage with their favorite causes and charitable organizations.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.funraise.org/giving-report\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-27204 size-large\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2020-Giving-Report-Promo-Graphic-2-1024x512.png?resize=960%2C480\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"480\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2020-Giving-Report-Promo-Graphic-2.png?resize=1024%2C512&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2020-Giving-Report-Promo-Graphic-2.png?resize=300%2C150&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2020-Giving-Report-Promo-Graphic-2.png?resize=768%2C384&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2020-Giving-Report-Promo-Graphic-2.png?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>In Italian:<br />\n<a href=\"https://italianonprofit.it/global-trends-in-giving-2020/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">2020 Global Trends in Giving Focus Italia</a></strong></p>\n<h3><strong>Previous Editions:</strong></h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2018-GivingReport-English.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">2018 Global Trends in Giving Report</a><br />\n</strong><strong><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2018-GivingReport-Spanish.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">2018 Informe sobre tendencias globales de donaci\u00f3n</a></strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2018-GivingReport-Portuguese.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>2018 Relat\u00f3rio Tend\u00eancias Globais de Doa\u00e7\u00f5es</strong></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2018-GivingReport-French.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>2018 rapport sur les tendances mondiales en mati\u00e8re de dons</strong></a></p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2017-Global-Trends-in-Giving-Report-English-Final.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">2017 Global Trends in Giving Report</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2017-Global-Trends-in-Giving-Report-Spanish-Final.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">2017 Informe sobre tendencias globales de donaci\u00f3n</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2017-Global-Trends-in-Giving-Report-French-Final.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">2017 rapport sur les tendances mondiales en mati\u00e8re de dons</a><br />\n</strong></p>\n<h2><strong>Global NGO Technology Report</strong></h2>\n<p>Released on September 16, 2019, the <a href=\"https://funraise.org/techreport\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>2019 Global NGO Technology Report</strong></a> examines how NGOs worldwide use web and email communications, online fundraising tools, social media, mobile technology, and productivity software.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://funraise.org/techreport\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-24306 size-full\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/2019-Global-NGO-Technology-Report-Blue-Small.png?resize=600%2C300\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/2019-Global-NGO-Technology-Report-Blue-Small.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/2019-Global-NGO-Technology-Report-Blue-Small.png?resize=300%2C150&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>In Spanish, Portuguese, and French:</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2019-Tech-Report-Spanish.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>2019 Informe Global sobre Tecnolog\u00eda de ONG</strong></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2019-Tech-Report-Portuguese.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>2019 Relat\u00f3rio Global de Tecnologia ONG</strong></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2019-Tech-Report-French.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>2019 rapport sur l\u2019utilisation des technologies par les organisations nongouvernementales (ONG) mondiales</strong></a></p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Previous Editions:</strong></h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2018-Tech-Report-English.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">2018 Global NGO Technology Report</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2018-Tech-Report-Spanish.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">2018 Informe Global sobre Tecnolog\u00eda de ONG</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2018-Tech-Report-Portuguese.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">2018 Relat\u00f3rio Global de Tecnologia ONG</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2018-Tech-Report-French.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">2018 rapport sur l\u2019utilisation des technologies par les organisations nongouvernementales (ONG) mondiales</a></strong></p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2017-Tech-Report-English-FINAL.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">2017 Global NGO Technology Report</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2017-NGO-Tech-Report_Spanish.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">2017 Informe Global sobre Tecnolog\u00eda de ONG</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2017-NGO-Tech-Report_French.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">2017 rapport sur l\u2019utilisation des technologies par les organisations nongouvernementales (ONG) mondiales</a></strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2016-Global-NGO-Online-Technology-Report-FINAL.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>2016 Global NGO Technology Report</strong></a></p>\n<hr />\n<p><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/heather-mansfield/\"><strong>Heather Mansfield</strong></a>, founder of Nonprofit Tech for Good, produces the Global NGO Technology Report and the Global Trends in Giving Report.\u00a0The findings from both reports are meant to help NGOs, nonprofits, and charities determine if they are effectively using technology to inspire philanthropy and achieve their mission and programs.</p>\n",
